Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好凉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没个像样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茜学校的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们学校里有像样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诗子你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 车来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就说嘛 再等等就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是诗子说天晴了要走着去的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉吃大亏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然就追上去？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追着公交跑就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊 你认识？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那人 穿的是你们学校的校服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这么个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.61,0:05:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茜 你真的不认识他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么会看到发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像忘了什么似的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天开始要晨练的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.78,0:05:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茜 我先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记了 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诗子 怎么会是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是茜嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正要去参加社团交流会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到是你 干嘛急急忙忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.39,0:08:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得有什么隐情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近的茜 总是无精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要她能打起精神就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 我只是听到这里传出了钢琴声
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正准备要弹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚才打开房门
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那会是谁弹的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.19,0:10:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真爱说笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 还没人用过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在等什么人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我常看到你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.89,0:12:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独自站在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和那人有约吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然不遵守和你的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你的... 约定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,画什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连环画
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个什么故事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.25,0:14:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柿子树和猴子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:15:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 一个不会爬树的小猴子的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是猴子 却不会爬树吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 小猴子在山里发现了一株完熟的柿子树
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它很想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 它不会爬树
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 为了得到柿子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它又是摇树 又是往树上丢石子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.37,0:15:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是得不到柿子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.52,0:15:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时候 樵夫叔叔出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到小猴子慌忙躲闪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樵夫好像也想吃柿子了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.83,0:15:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樵夫从砍倒的树上摘走了一些柿子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就快步下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好过分哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.84,0:15:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就为了几个柿子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:16:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小猴子可以随便拿剩下的柿子了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 它怎么不带走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.19,0:16:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是诗子你 来这里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了对了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 值周日志
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么是你来送
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交流会上对手校的人拜托我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我得去参加社团活动了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周开始就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折原... 浩平...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折原浩平... 君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.47,0:19:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来... 你还记得我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在等 我青梅竹马的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青梅竹马...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.55,0:19:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么永远 根本就不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.17,0:20:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远 是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它就在这里...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再过不久 这片空地就要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能送出去的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你听我说了这么久 请收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的生日是几号
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次 换我来等待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.64,0:21:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一言为定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.64,0:22:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 是茜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.23,0:22:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撞我就不要紧了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.78,0:22:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 你新画的连环画呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.42,0:22:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进展顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.92,0:23:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,画好后再让我看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.92,0:23:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得赶去社团活动了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.51,0:23:10.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰上君 你的技艺又进步了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.13,0:23:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于记住我的名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.76,0:23:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在特殊的日子里一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.54,0:23:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？ 谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.95,0:23:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折原 浩平
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.61,0:23:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这么一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.51,0:24:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 想不起来就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.15,0:24:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 马上就是音乐大赛了吧
